name: Birds Vs Aliens
description:
Eat your food and don't starve, but wait ALIENS want your food too!!

How To Play

Move you mouse around to make the bird follow you and eat the worms

Every 5 seconds your points deplete by 1, if it reaches to 0 you are DEAD

That's not all, there are ALIENS in their UFO waiting to steal your food

So DON'T STOP MOVING.
